     Deposit liquidity, borrow USD.

     Structure of all Cygnus Contracts:

     Contract                        ⠀Interface                                             
        ├ 1. Libraries                   ├ 1. Custom Errors                                               
        ├ 2. Storage                     ├ 2. Custom Events
